\par\par \b \uc2 New law to bring issuance of local  \highlight22\uc2 taxes \highlight\uc2  into line   \b0\par\par\uc2 Urip Hudiono , The Jakarta Post, Jakarta   \par \uc2 483 \uc2 words\par \uc2 13 April 2006\par \uc2 The Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par 2\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2006 The Jakarta Post   \par \par \uc2 The government, in another effort to improve the country's investment climate, has completed a new bill prohibiting regions from arbitrarily imposing local \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 The draft regional \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  and user charges law, which was submitted to the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  for deliberation last month, also strictly regulates existing local \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2 , particularly on their maximum rates.   \par \par \uc2 "The law is expected to close any loopholes for regions to issue other `problematic' \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2 ," head of the Finance Ministry's \b \highlight22\uc2 Economic\b0 \highlight\uc2 , Financial and International Collaboration Studies Agency (Bapekki), Anggito Abimanyu, said Wednesday.   \par \par \uc2 "We therefore expect it to help improve the investment climate as well, because we know such \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  have been the main discouragement for investors."   \par \par \uc2 Anggito explained that local administrations would no longer be able to impose local \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  or user charges without providing the legal basis for them through related local regulations.   \par \par \uc2 The regulations must be submitted to both the Finance Ministry and Home Ministry for review and approval, with the central government having the right to impose sanctions on local administrations refusing to revoke \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  deemed unfit or with higher rates than the new law allows.   \par \par \uc2 "Sanctions will be related to a region's general allocation funds," Anggito said, referring to the funds allocated to local administrations from the central government's annual state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 Anggito said the bill also would try to strike a balance in maintaining adequate local revenue for the regions, with high revenue-generating \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  on motor vehicles and street lighting still allowed.   \par \par \uc2 "A new environmental \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  also will be introduced, while certain \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2 , such as the underground water \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2 , will be delegated from the provinces to regencies and city administrations," he said.   \par \par \uc2 According to a draft of the law obtained by The Jakarta Post , the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on automobiles will be reduced from the current 5 percent to between 1-3 percent, with items of trains and heavy equipment, among others, exempt from \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2 . The underground water \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  is set at a maximum 20 percent and the environment \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  at 0.5 percent of production costs.   \par \par \uc2 The Home Ministry revoked last month 537 out of a 5,054 local regulations submitted for review by the Finance Ministry. The total \b \highlight22\uc2 regulation\b0 \highlight\uc2  reviewed is, however, still only 37 percent of the 13,520 regulations issued by 30 provinces and 370 regencies throughout the country.   \par \par \uc2 The business community has long complained about local \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  and user charges imposed on them after the introduction of the autonomy law in 1999, which has fueled a high-cost \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 The World Bank's recent Doing Business in 2006 report puts legal \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  resulting from regional autonomy -- including a surfeit of local \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  and user charges -- among the top factors discouraging investors.   \par \par \uc2 The central government also faced difficulties in setting a time frame to review and annul controversial bylaws deemed controversial.   \par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020060413e24d00009\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
